column5: This morning over Clear Lake from my front porch
beauty pic Lew
Yes Lew he sure does , did you know it is also his way of saying , Red Skys in the morning Sailors & fisherman better take warning .
Awesome!......A picture is worth a thousand words..
Thanks Lew. I drank my coffee this morning with your pic.
Amazing what mother nature can do...  Thanks...
lew. thats amazing. as we have more life experiences we notice all of the good things. thanks for sharing.
Nice pic thanks for posting Lew
Just beautiful
It is like God is smiling for you in the morning  Nice picture Lew.
Thanks folks, glad you enjoyed the picture.  Too bad that kinda stuff only last a few minutes.
indeed. Hard to look around and deny His existence.
Lew if I can add please He does great work here in MIssissauga also.
wow that's a beauty too
Took this out on Lake O..   Thank the city of Toronto for the smog, lol!
That's a couple more beautiful pictures guys, thanks for adding them to the post.  Anyone else have anymore to add ??
Taken back home .
My view this morning Lew.  One of the best sunrises I've seen in a while.

I think we were looking at the same place at the same time this morning Will. Just above and to the left of your rising sun there's a clear patch in the clouds. You'll see the same thing in my picture.
Mine are quantity over quality, lol.  Awesome pics guys, thanks for sharing!
Incredible pictures guys  Lew, you should blow that picture up and hang it up on the wall...Just amazing
Nothing like a beautiful sunrise!! We saw beautiful sunsets every night in Vallarta, but I still prefer a nice sunrise to start the day.
Ditto---that's what I'd do.
I've framed a couple that turned out nice, here's one I like.
Looking at the same time for sure Lew, but wasn't in your area. Pretty cool that we captured it pretty much at the same time.
